'''张力原纤维'''（{{lang-en|tonofibril}}）是[[上皮組織|上皮組織]]中的胞質蛋白結構，聚集在[[橋粒|橋粒]]和{{tsl|en|hemidesmosomes|半桥粒}}上，<ref name=":0">{{DorlandsDict|eight/000109361|tonofibril}}</ref>由錨定在[[細胞骨架|細胞骨架]]上皮細胞中的細纖維組成。<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Filaggrin in the frontline: role in skin barrier function and disease|last=Sandilands|first=Aileen|last2=Sutherland|first2=Calum|date=2009-05-01|journal=J Cell Sci|issue=9|doi=10.1242/jcs.033969|volume=122|pages=1285–1294|issn=0021-9533|pmc=2721001|pmid=19386895|last3=Irvine|first3=Alan D.|last4=McLean|first4=W. H. Irwin}}</ref>张力原纤维由[[鲁道夫·海登海因|鲁道夫·海登海因]]发现，于1897年由[[路易-安托万·朗维埃|路易-安托万·朗维埃]]首次进行详细描述。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Tonofibrils of the Human Epidermis1|url=http://www.nature.com/jid/journal/v29/n5/full/jid1957108a.html#tlnote1|last=Charles|first=Arwyn|last2=Smiddy|first2=F. G.|date=1957-09-01|journal=Journal of Investigative Dermatology|issue=5|doi=10.1038/jid.1957.108|volume=29|pages=327–338|issn=0022-202X|pmid=13502588|access-date=2020-12-04|archive-date=2016-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122133524/http://www.nature.com/jid/journal/v29/n5/full/jid1957108a.html#tlnote1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 組成 ==
张力原纤维是由张力丝（{{lang-en|tonofilament}}）构成的。张力丝与桥粒相连，是一种由[[角蛋白|角蛋白]]构成的直径为10[[纳米|纳米]]的[[中间纤维|中间丝]]。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/title/xi-bao-sheng-wu-xue-ming-ci-2009-chinese-terms-in-cell-biology/oclc/500845140&referer=brief_results|publisher=科学出版社|date=2009|location=北京|isbn=978-7-03-024924-1|oclc=500845140|language=zh|title=细胞生物学名词}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/title/zu-zhi-xue-yu-pei-tai-xue-ming-ci-chinese-terms-in-histology-and-embryology-2014/oclc/1102566470&referer=brief_results|date=2014|isbn=978-7-03-040573-9|oclc=1102566470|language=zh|last=人体解剖学与组织胚胎学名词审定委员会|title=组织学与胚胎学名词}}</ref>

